# M6 m6-pickup-placement — visual proof that aurora's central pit
# is now a carved basin with reachable pickups, and the east mountain-
# peak rail cannon sits on the exposed summit (not buried in the rise
# tile body).
#
# Pre-fix the 5 pit pickups at y = floor_pick + 64 = 2800 sat inside
# the still-solid floor tiles; the central pit was BACKGROUND-poly
# decoration only. Post-fix cols 74..86 rows 86..87 are carved EMPTY
# so the pickups inhabit a real 2-tile-deep basin.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/m6_placement_aurora
seed 1 2

map aurora

# Spawn at the central-pit lip (col 73, just west of the carve) so
# the camera frames the new basin shape on its first shot.
spawn_at 2336 2712

contact_sheet placement_aurora cols 3 cell 426 240

at 1   shot t1_pit_overview
at 60  shot t60_settled

# Walk right into the carved basin.
at 80  press right
at 130 release right
at 160 shot t160_inside_pit
at 200 end
